posting_body: ['2 Weeks Free Look and Lease Special +$1000 OFF Move in Special!', 'Royal Sepulveda', '6920 Sepulveda Boulevard, Van Nuys, CA 91405', 'Call ☏ :', 'show contact info', 'Welcome to Royal Sepulveda Apartment Homes!', 'Enjoy community amenities such as a sparkling swimming pool, plenty of parking, and on-site laundry.', 'Come home to your comfortable studio apartment with air conditioning, a built-in dresser, a gas stove, and a refrigerator.', 'Royal Sepulveda Apartment Homes are in a prime location close to the 405 Freeway, public transportation, shopping and restaurants.', 'Stop by today and say hello to our professional management staff and find your new home!', 'Community Amenities:', '- Laundry Facility', '- Bike Racks', '- On-Site Manager', '- Easy Access to Shopping', '- On-Call Maintenance', '- Swimming Pool', '- Courtyard', '- Close to Public Transportation', '- Spacious Floor Plans', '- Close to the 405 Freeway', 'Apartment Amenities:', '- Large Closets', '- Gas Range', '- Disposal', '- Built-In Dresser', '- Carpeting', '- Air Conditioning', '- Refrigerator', 'Square Footage Is Approximate.', 'Price and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not be of exact unit.']
